                                memes when I'm at my absolute wildest and
                                silliest
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </column>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <column>
                        <row gap-="1">
                            <strong>Github</strong>
                            <span>{'•'}</span>
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/IroncladDev"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noreferrer">
                                github.com/IroncladDev
                            </a>
                        </row>
                        <ul pad-="1 0" marker-="open tree">
                            <li>
                                <row gap-="1">
                                    <span
                                        is-="badge"
                                        variant-="green-bg"
                                        cap-="triangle">
                                        󰔛 Response Time
                                    </span>
                                    <span style="color: var(--yellow-fg)"
                                        >Mid</span
                                    >
                                </row>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <row gap-="1">
                                    <span
                                        is-="badge"
                                        variant-="purple-bg"
                                        cap-="triangle">
                                        󰄨 Usage
                                    </span>
                                    <span style="color: var(--green-fg-dim)"
                                        >Frequent</span
                                    >
                                </row>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The home of my open source projects. I usually
